{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"16":"Sacrifice (Kitab Al-Dahaya)"},"section_detail":{"16":{"hadithnumber_first":2788,"hadithnumber_last":2843,"arabicnumber_first":2788,"arabicnumber_last":2843}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2811,"arabicnumber":2811,"text":"حدثنا عثمان بن ابي شيبة، ان ابا اسامة، حدثهم عن اسامة، عن نافع، عن ابن عمر، ان النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم كان يذبح اضحيته بالمصلى وكان ابن عمر يفعله","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":16,"hadith":24}}]}